      "description": "Check out this dependable daily driver that\u2019s ready to get you where you need to go! This car has served its previous owners well and still offers a solid, functional ride for anyone looking for great value. While it shows some expected wear and tear consistent with its age, it remains a practical choice for budget-conscious buyers who prioritize utility and character.",
