      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in poor condition and is being sold strictly as-is. It currently has significant mechanical issues, including a rough-running engine and a transmission that slips, meaning it will likely need a tow or major repairs before it can be used as a reliable daily driver. The exterior has multiple large dents, peeling clear coat, and some rust spots, while the interior shows heavy wear, including torn upholstery and non-functional electronics. This would be an ideal project for a mechanic or a source for parts.",
