      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "Presenting a truly collector-grade example that defies its age. This vehicle has been meticulously preserved in a climate-controlled environment, showcasing a mirror-like finish with zero rock chips or imperfections. Inside, the cabin remains in showroom condition; the premium leather seats show no bolster wear, and the original factory scent lingers. Every service has been performed ahead of schedule by certified technicians, with a complete folder of maintenance records included. From the flawless alloy wheels wrapped in fresh performance tires to the pristine, dust-free engine bay, this car looks and drives as if it just rolled off the assembly line. A rare find for the discerning enthusiast who demands absolute perfection.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 5
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_5_listing_5",
